[[uid=830lwb7l]] the next room for a moment. [[attitudeInstr]]
[[uid=830lwb7m]] 
[[uid=830lwb7n]] LADY BRACKNELL.
[[uid=830lwb7p]] Thank you, Algernon. It is very
[[uid=830lwb7q]] thoughtful of you. [Rising, and
[[uid=830lwb7r]] following Algernon.] I’m sure the
[[uid=830lwb7s]] programme will be delightful, after a
